142:     <div class="gauge" id="gauge"></div>
143:     <div class="meta">
144:       <h2>Looking for Healthy — overall quality</h2>
145:       <p>Weighted pass-rate across the 15 structural DCMA-14 checks. The remaining
146:          metrics (CPLI, BEI and checks #18–22) are reported standalone and are not folded into this roll-up.</p>
147:       <div class="legend">
148:         <div class="lg"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--good)"></span>Excellent ≥ 85%</div>
149:         <div class="lg"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--neutral)"></span>Moderate 70–85%</div>
